        oDeleteStatusBar (StatusBar, EraseMode)
                             A0          D0

        void oDeleteStatusBar (struct oStatusBar *, long)

  FUNCTION
        This function frees a Status Bar object created using @{"oCreateStatusBarA()" link "oCreateStatusBarA()"}.

  INPUTS
