        oMsgInfo  -- varargs stub for oMsgInfoA()

  SYNOPSIS
        oMsgInfoA (TitleText, BodyText, Argv)
                       A0        A1      A2

        oMsgInfo  (TitleText, BodyText, ...)

        void oMsgInfoA (STRPTR, STRPTR, long *)

        void oMsgInfo  (STRPTR, STRPTR, ...)

  FUNCTION
        This function opens an information requester displaying the passed
